=== Blood Pressure Abnormalities
<subsec:blood-pressure>

*Clinical Presentation.*

    - Orthostatic hypotension (blood pressure drops upon standing)
    - Labile blood pressure (large fluctuations)
    - Hypertension in some patients
    - Symptoms of inadequate perfusion (dizziness, vision changes, syncope)
